1. Introduction to SPSA
========================

Please see the following for the implementation of SPSA.
https://github.com/zamar/spsa


2. Modifications of SPSA
========================

- comparison between test, plus and minus instead between plus and minus
- introduction of an objective (cost) function: 1 / (1 + 10 ** (d / 400)) where d is difference in result between master and test
- making a and c parameters dependent on cost

3. Configuration file
=====================

psqt.var contains all parameters from stockfish piece-square tables